dmenu - dynamic menu
====================
dmenu is an efficient dynamic menu for X.

Patches
-------
- Added center patch <https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/patches/center/>.
- Added border patch <https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/patches/border/>.
- Added grid patch <https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/patches/grid/>.
- Added gridnav patch <https://tools.suckless.org/dmenu/patches/gridnav/>.

Requirements
------------
In order to build dmenu you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Edit config.mk to match your local setup (dmenu is installed into
the /usr/local namespace by default).

Afterwards enter the following command to build and install dmenu
(if necessary as root):

    make clean install


Running dmenu
-------------
See the man page for details.
